      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained over the years. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission provides reliable shifting, making it a dependable choice for your daily commute or longer trips. While it shows light signs of careful use, the interior remains clean and the mechanical components are in solid working order. Buyers can expect a car that is ready for the road with no immediate major repairs required.",
