    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age in several areas. The exterior has some noticeable scratches and minor dings consistent with regular use, and the interior upholstery shows signs of wear, including some fading and small stains. Mechanically, it runs and drives, but the suspension is a bit soft and it will likely need routine maintenance soon, such as new tires and a brake service. All major electronics are functional, though the air conditioning takes a moment to get cold. It is a solid, honest car for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind a bit of character.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a reliable source for parts? This vehicle is in poor condition and ready for some serious mechanical attention, making it the perfect canvas for a car lover who enjoys a challenge! While it needs significant work, it offers a fantastic opportunity to get hands-on and bring a car back to life at a budget-friendly price.",
